{"tid":1685124,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[發動技能]執到隻bb貓，求高手指教","createTime":"2019-10-31T11:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T02:40:09.000Z","uid":34978,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4709062496d56b26afef2522ee3107ab86da7d","tid":1685124,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:32:39.000Z","msg":"發動技能執到隻bb貓<br />\n唔知幾大，目測細過2個月<br />\n有個喺附近返工嘅姨姨餵開<br />\n話佢應該係冇貓媽湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為呢到成日有人除草同殺蟲<br />\n加上天氣轉涼驚佢咁細捱唔住<br />\n就決定接佢回家<br />\n<br />\n家有養緊一隻貓（一歲幾貓女）<br />\n所以貓用品有齊，窗網當然都有<br />\n屋企嗰隻2個半月大開始養佢，當時已戒奶<br />\n所以冇養咁細貓b嘅經驗<br />\n打算聽朝帶細貓睇醫生，同買貓奶<br />\n仲有咩要注意？請教連登貓高手指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8971ba788f606979014c5485283245b2ed25264c","tid":1685124,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:36:41.000Z","msg":"（公投）11.2好似有活動撞左時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1685128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1685128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手入嚟睇下討論下推下啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf6067c3b8ee2b4437511f7f681fa9ea31c87c8","tid":1685124,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:37:53.000Z","msg":"最好困佢係籠到適應下先<br />\n因為你唔知屋企果隻對佢有幾大反應"},{"pid":"9344b73896bce6132d08044bf5ccbc9e654cbe20","tid":1685124,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2e1fce267f249985c9f2ec383cd97127e74f64","tid":1685124,"uid":34978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"